trans-unit.source: Represents an extensibility element added to an <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.InputBinding" /> or an <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.OutputBinding" /> within an XML Web service, specifying the MIME format for the body of the HTTP transmission.
This class cannot be inherited.
For more information about specifying protocols for XML Web services, see [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).
trans-unit.target: 如需有關指定的 XML Web 服務通訊協定的詳細資訊，請參閱[ [ \<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices >]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c)。

trans-unit.source: For more information about Web Services Description Language (WSDL), see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: 如需 Web 服務描述語言 (WSDL) 的詳細資訊，請參閱規格的http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/。

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates the use of the properties and methods exposed by the `MimeContentBinding` class.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例示範如何使用的屬性和方法所公開`MimeContentBinding`類別。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeContentBinding" /> class.
Specifies the URI for the XML namespace of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeContentBinding" /> class.
This field is constant.
Gets or sets the name of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> to which the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeContentBinding" /> applies.

A string representing the name of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" /> with which the current <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeContentBinding" /> is associated.
trans-unit.target: 表示名稱的字串<see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MessagePart" />與其目前<see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.MimeContentBinding" />相關聯。

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
Gets or sets a value indicating the format of the body of the HTTP transmission.
A string indicating the format of the body of the HTTP transmission.
trans-unit.target: 表示 HTTP 傳輸主體的格式字串。

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").

The Web Services Description Language (WSDL) specification defines bindings for several MIME types, including text/xml, multipart/related, and application/x-www-form-urlencoded, although any MIME type can be used.
trans-unit.target: Web 服務描述語言 (WSDL) 規格中定義數個 MIME 類型，包括 text/xml、 multipart/related 以及應用程式/x-www-表單-urlencoded，雖然可以用任何 MIME 類型的繫的結。

trans-unit.source: The wildcard character (*) can also be used.
For example, the string "text/\*" would represent all text types.
trans-unit.target: 例如，字串"文字 /\*"代表所有文字類型。

trans-unit.source: If the value of this property is not set, the `MimeContentBinding` specifies all MIME types.
trans-unit.target: 如果未設定這個屬性的值，`MimeContentBinding`指定所有的 MIME 類型。

trans-unit.source: For more information about WSDL, see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: 如需有關 WSDL 的詳細資訊，請參閱規格的http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/。
